news_header: FSB arrests four near Russia-Finland border, none are Russian nationals.
news_original_title: Venäläismediat: Venäjän rajavartijat ottivat keskiviikkona kiinni neljä Suomeen pyrkinyttä
news_text: The Russian FSB has arrested four individuals near the Russia-Finland border, reportedly attempting to reach Finland. None of the detainees are Russian nationals. The incident occurred in Vyborg, and the FSB released video footage showing the arrests. The Southeast Finnish Border Guard has not commented on their involvement.
